33:57.422 --> 33:59.382
...to keep out people like us.

33:59.502 --> 34:04.143
lt's all so ironic and amusing, okay?
Now, how do we get in?

34:05.703 --> 34:06.863
We can't.

34:07.863 --> 34:09.503
You can't get in the panic room.

34:09.623 --> 34:13.103
That's the whole point.
We have to get her to come out.

34:13.663 --> 34:15.303
And why would she do that?

34:16.143 --> 34:17.382
l don't know.

34:18.264 --> 34:21.424
But when she does,
she can't get out of this house.

34:22.463 --> 34:25.623
We keep her here,
we keep her quiet for 20 minutes...

34:25.862 --> 34:28.743
...and l don't want any help
from Joe Pesci over here.

34:29.464 --> 34:31.984
They want to hole up in this house? Fine.

34:32.263 --> 34:34.463
We make it impossible for them to leave.

34:37.184 --> 34:39.824
And why would they come out
in the first place?

34:42.024 --> 34:43.704
l'm working on that.

34:51.543 --> 34:53.664
-Are you okay?
-Yeah.

34:56.625 --> 34:57.985
Small space?

34:58.665 --> 34:59.905
l'm okay.

35:01.425 --> 35:02.825
-You can't wig out.
-l know.

35:02.945 --> 35:04.585
-l mean it.
-l won't.

35:07.345 --> 35:10.305
You know,
people never get buried alive anymore.

35:11.985 --> 35:14.226
l guess it used to happen all the time.

35:15.186 --> 35:16.426
Really?

35:16.665 --> 35:18.025
Yeah, l read that.

35:19.185 --> 35:21.425
And when did this happen all the time?

35:23.826 --> 35:25.826
Twenty, thirty years ago.

35:28.826 --> 35:30.585
What are they doing now?

35:36.786 --> 35:38.306
l don't know.

36:36.508 --> 36:38.068
They're locking us in.

37:15.750 --> 37:17.510
This is not happening.

37:27.709 --> 37:29.070
Sarah, calm down.

37:31.190 --> 37:34.350
You know what could happen
if you let yourself get worked up.

37:35.511 --> 37:36.710
Sarah!

38:05.272 --> 38:08.351
-What the hell are you doing?
-We're coming in from below.

38:08.591 --> 38:11.832
No, you're not. Even if you got through
the concrete, there's steel.

38:11.911 --> 38:13.591
You won't even make a dent.

38:14.432 --> 38:15.672
We'll see.

38:16.991 --> 38:19.031
Hey. This is what l do.

38:19.311 --> 38:22.031
lf some idiot with a sledgehammer
could break in...

38:22.311 --> 38:25.112
...do you really think
that l would still have a job?

38:33.712 --> 38:35.432
Don't get that in your eye.

39:08.433 --> 39:09.594
Neighbor.

39:09.833 --> 39:10.993
Help!

39:11.153 --> 39:13.314
Please help us!

39:13.873 --> 39:15.793
-Call the police!
-Do you hear us?

39:16.233 --> 39:17.234
Help us!

39:28.434 --> 39:29.594
Help!

39:29.834 --> 39:32.634
-Help us, please!
-Call the police!

40:14.795 --> 40:16.076
Shit!

40:42.157 --> 40:44.156
You guys just going to stand there?

40:44.676 --> 40:46.837
Why? What do you got, MacGyver?

41:20.318 --> 41:22.758
He can't get in here with a hammer,
can he?

41:28.959 --> 41:31.078
Could you be any louder?

41:41.039 --> 41:42.919
Give me a hand with those boxes.

41:45.079 --> 41:46.439
Listen, goddamn it!

41:46.839 --> 41:49.959
l'm in charge here.
Now, what the hell is going on?

41:55.639 --> 41:58.880
-They're going to get in here.
-No, they can't get in here.

42:02.359 --> 42:05.000
We're going to be fine. We'll be just fine.

43:08.601 --> 43:09.922
Oh, this is good.

43:11.642 --> 43:12.961
This could work.

43:13.202 --> 43:16.282
l was just thinking
that we should do something like this.

43:20.282 --> 43:23.042
-Open it.
-l just did.

43:23.162 --> 43:24.922
Open it some more.

43:26.602 --> 43:28.762
We're just sending them a message.

43:29.923 --> 43:31.402
They'll get the point.

44:07.724 --> 44:09.444
Honey, get down on the ground.

44:17.764 --> 44:20.964
Quit dicking around
and open this fucking thing up.

44:21.044 --> 44:23.084
-Don't be stupid.
-Quiet!

44:23.204 --> 44:25.684
We're trying to scare them, not kill them.

44:32.485 --> 44:33.845
What is it?

44:34.564 --> 44:35.524
lt's bad.

44:37.604 --> 44:39.005
They're coughing.

44:39.365 --> 44:41.525
lf they're coughing, they're going to die!

44:41.645 --> 44:43.205
Nobody is going to die, man!

44:43.285 --> 44:46.485
Will you please have the balls
to follow through with something?

45:01.166 --> 45:02.285
Mom.

45:06.525 --> 45:09.926
The worst that'll happen is they'll pass out.
They'll have a hangover.

45:10.006 --> 45:13.086
How are we going to get in there
if they pass out, Junior?

45:15.606 --> 45:16.807
Cut it back a little.

45:16.886 --> 45:19.766
They won't pass out, numb-nuts.
They'll throw up first.

45:19.926 --> 45:21.846
We can't get in if they're dead!

45:24.366 --> 45:26.206
Stay on the ground and breathe.

45:32.766 --> 45:34.167
Turn it down.

45:34.887 --> 45:36.287
Turn it down! lt's too much!

45:36.446 --> 45:38.847
-Don't you start up with this shit.
-Keep it down!

45:49.527 --> 45:50.727
l'm turning it down.

45:50.808 --> 45:53.207
-Keep his ass off of me.
-We're not killing anybody.

46:04.088 --> 46:06.248
-Tell him to turn it down!
-Turn the shit off.

46:06.848 --> 46:08.488
-No.
-Turn it down.

46:19.769 --> 46:21.648
-Mom?
-Just a second.

46:26.008 --> 46:27.169
Get under this.

46:28.848 --> 46:29.889
Oh, my god.

46:30.129 --> 46:32.688
-Fucking amateurs, man!
-lt's my fucking idea.

46:42.369 --> 46:45.649
Shut the fuck up!
There are people trying to sleep over there.

47:09.250 --> 47:10.490
What is that?

47:12.010 --> 47:13.370
Turn the gas off.

47:22.171 --> 47:23.970
Turn the gas off right now.

47:46.651 --> 47:47.932
Get back!

47:48.531 --> 47:49.651
Shit!

47:52.452 --> 47:53.731
God!

47:53.852 --> 47:55.092
Get it off me!

48:01.252 --> 48:02.412
lt's okay.

48:04.972 --> 48:09.452
You fucking bitch! You fucking bitch!
l'm coming in there!

48:10.492 --> 48:12.492
Calm the fuck down.

48:22.292 --> 48:24.133
-Are you okay?
-Yeah.

48:25.653 --> 48:29.933
Promise me you'll never do
anything like that.

48:30.893 --> 48:32.053
l won't.

48:34.853 --> 48:38.174
They're moving.
At least they're still moving in there.

48:50.054 --> 48:51.054
What?

48:51.734 --> 48:52.974
Talk to him.

48:55.934 --> 48:58.213
Please, man, give it a rest.

49:56.936 --> 49:59.056
-That Morse code?
-SOS.

49:59.296 --> 50:00.816
Where'd you learn that?

50:01.056 --> 50:02.296
Titanic.

50:13.217 --> 50:15.216
We got to talk. Downstairs.

50:21.096 --> 50:23.377
No, no, no. Not you.

50:29.617 --> 50:32.937
Come on, come on, come on.

50:34.217 --> 50:35.417
Get up.

50:36.538 --> 50:37.778
Come on.

50:46.577 --> 50:47.857
Wake up.

50:53.098 --> 50:56.818
The first thing l'm going to do this morning
is call my plastic surgeon.

50:56.898 --> 51:01.698
There's been a change here.
$100,000 is not enough. Not for this shit.

51:02.938 --> 51:05.738
l want a third
of whatever's in that room up there.

51:09.778 --> 51:10.699
Fine!

51:10.819 --> 51:14.939
Okay? Full share, one-third.
Congratulations.

51:15.538 --> 51:19.539
You bought a ski mask, made $1,000,000.
Your parents will be proud.

51:41.019 --> 51:42.220
Got him.

51:42.699 --> 51:46.500
Let me straighten out something else.
Get control of your goddamn expert.

51:46.740 --> 51:48.979
l'm not losing
my half of the money because--

51:49.100 --> 51:50.499
Slow down. Half?

51:50.619 --> 51:53.900
Did you sleep through grade school?
Five seconds ago, it was a third....

51:54.820 --> 51:56.020
Come on.

52:00.940 --> 52:03.060
l'm letting you know he's a problem.

52:03.300 --> 52:05.940
But this wasn't my idea,
so he's your problem.

52:06.101 --> 52:08.260
You're right. lt wasn't your idea!

52:08.380 --> 52:10.420
None of this was your idea!
lt was my idea!

52:13.781 --> 52:15.460
Come on, look over here.

52:27.501 --> 52:28.541
Yes.

52:29.381 --> 52:30.621
Yes, yes, yes.

52:34.101 --> 52:36.341
Let's hope this guy's an ex-Boy Scout.

52:42.341 --> 52:44.021
-We're here!
-Help us!

52:44.102 --> 52:45.822
We're over here!

52:55.902 --> 52:57.062
Help!

52:57.222 --> 52:59.262
Open your window!

52:59.422 --> 53:00.622
Help!

53:08.822 --> 53:11.022
We're never going to get out of here.

53:19.143 --> 53:22.263
l'm the loving grandson who put in
the time with the old man...

53:22.383 --> 53:24.663
...every goddamn weekend for two years...

53:24.863 --> 53:27.743
...talking to him, dressing him,
walking him, feeding him.

53:27.903 --> 53:29.263
Are you done?

53:29.383 --> 53:32.504
No. l'm the one the old man
finally told about the safe.

53:32.623 --> 53:36.303
l'm the one who found the guy who built it,
and l convinced him to break into it!

53:39.863 --> 53:41.063
Wait a minute.

53:44.063 --> 53:47.184
-What?
-The bedroom's empty. Where are they?

53:49.304 --> 53:50.984
Two of them, on the stairs.

53:51.743 --> 53:53.224
Where's the third guy?

53:57.104 --> 53:59.024
l left my cell phone by the bed.

54:03.385 --> 54:04.784
l earned that money.

54:05.145 --> 54:07.465
l will not let you jeopardize
my fucking plan...

54:07.625 --> 54:10.745
...because you have a problem
relating to others!

54:12.265 --> 54:13.465
Got it?

54:14.784 --> 54:16.825
lf l don't come back, close this door.

54:16.905 --> 54:18.624
Just do what l say.

54:20.865 --> 54:22.705
He touches me again, l'll shoot him.

54:22.785 --> 54:23.785
Christ!

54:26.185 --> 54:27.305
Wait!

54:30.666 --> 54:33.865
Any other schoolyard bullshit to settle,
or can we get back to work?

54:34.346 --> 54:36.185
Don't take no tone with me, jerk-wad.

54:36.385 --> 54:39.105
l'll shove it up your ass and snap it off.

54:39.225 --> 54:42.466
You're a bus driver, Raoul.

54:42.905 --> 54:44.186
You live in Flatbush.

54:44.305 --> 54:47.025
Don't spout some Elmore Leonard
bullshit you just heard...

54:47.305 --> 54:48.986
...because l saw that movie, too.

54:49.426 --> 54:50.346
What is this?

54:52.546 --> 54:53.906
l got some news for you.

54:56.106 --> 54:57.427
Go.

54:57.666 --> 54:59.026
Go!

56:43.470 --> 56:44.350
Fuck!

56:46.350 --> 56:48.830
She got something. What did she get?

56:49.950 --> 56:50.830
No.

56:52.910 --> 56:54.031
Charger!

56:54.750 --> 56:56.790
She has a cell phone.

56:58.271 --> 56:59.191
No!

57:01.070 --> 57:02.351
All right, signal.

57:02.590 --> 57:05.150
Come on. Signal.

57:16.271 --> 57:19.511
l don't think they'll be talking
on no cell phone from in there.

57:20.551 --> 57:23.071
-Why not?
-You can't call out from in there.

57:25.911 --> 57:27.352
No signal.

57:36.591 --> 57:39.232
l didn't hook up this line,
but l hooked up the main line.

57:39.352 --> 57:41.752
lf we can find it, we can cut into it.

57:43.672 --> 57:48.272
l can't go to prison, man.
l'm not built for that shit.

57:59.112 --> 58:00.072
Be careful.

58:11.153 --> 58:12.353
Get the phone.

58:12.553 --> 58:14.553
-lt doesn't come off.
-Rip it off!

58:25.634 --> 58:27.714
Screwdriver. Phillips.

58:34.914 --> 58:38.954
Junior, when l asked you to cut
the phone lines, did you cut the main line?

58:39.314 --> 58:42.394
Or did you just cut the cord on the phone
in the kitchen?

59:07.355 --> 59:08.194
Shit!

59:11.115 --> 59:13.155
Strip this and expose the wires.

59:13.275 --> 59:15.395
-What are we doing?
-l have no idea.

59:42.356 --> 59:44.836
-Okay, got it?
-Yeah. Here.

59:45.077 --> 59:46.116
Okay.

59:46.596 --> 59:48.116
Yellow, yellow.

01:00:01.917 --> 01:00:02.796
Okay.

01:00:05.116 --> 01:00:06.277
Dial tone.

01:00:14.997 --> 01:00:16.198
911 emergency.

01:00:16.437 --> 01:00:18.997
Yes, this is 38 West 94th Street--

01:00:19.117 --> 01:00:22.157
-pIease hoId.
-No, no. God.

01:00:27.598 --> 01:00:28.478
Call Dad.

01:00:33.398 --> 01:00:37.038
How do you live in New York
and not have a single Percocet?

01:00:39.318 --> 01:00:42.318
-HeIIo?
-Stephan. Put Stephan on the line.

01:00:42.438 --> 01:00:44.199
-Who is this?
-lt's Meg.

01:00:45.038 --> 01:00:46.598
Do you know what time it is?

01:00:46.998 --> 01:00:50.118
-Put him on the phone, bitch.
-It's your fucking wife.

01:00:53.958 --> 01:00:54.879
Move.

01:00:56.958 --> 01:00:59.199
-HeIIo?
-You've got to help us.

01:00:59.279 --> 01:01:00.199
Move!

01:01:00.439 --> 01:01:03.559
There are three men upstairs.
They broke in--

01:01:06.839 --> 01:01:07.719
What--

01:01:22.320 --> 01:01:24.119
-He'll do something.
-No, he won't.

01:01:24.240 --> 01:01:25.680
He'll call the police.

01:01:25.919 --> 01:01:27.880
You don't know her. She won't let him.

01:01:28.160 --> 01:01:31.360
No. He knows that there's trouble.
He heard me.

01:01:32.160 --> 01:01:35.360
He's across the park. That's why
we got houses close to each other.

01:01:35.480 --> 01:01:37.800
Just in case we needed each other.
He'll help us.

01:01:37.920 --> 01:01:40.080
-He won't.
-Yes, he will!

01:01:45.840 --> 01:01:47.080
l'm sorry.

01:01:47.640 --> 01:01:49.400
No, l'm sorry.

01:01:50.561 --> 01:01:51.481
Why?

01:01:52.881 --> 01:01:54.720
l was trying not to tell you.

01:01:55.921 --> 01:01:56.841
What?

01:01:57.521 --> 01:01:59.361
l'm dizzy and hungry.

01:02:02.521 --> 01:02:05.601
All she's got is NyQuil and fucking Midol.

01:02:08.002 --> 01:02:10.322
Looks like that gas idea
didn't work so well.

01:02:11.041 --> 01:02:12.361
Whose fault was that?

01:02:12.561 --> 01:02:13.801
This is impossible.

01:02:14.042 --> 01:02:15.601
What's the plan now, hot rod?

01:02:15.721 --> 01:02:18.282
This is worse than impossible.
This is unpleasant.

01:02:20.322 --> 01:02:22.961
Here, drink this.
All right, drink lots of water.

01:02:23.642 --> 01:02:26.882
You dropped to the low 40s.
We have to get your blood-sugar up.

01:02:26.961 --> 01:02:28.402
Can you hear me okay?

01:02:28.522 --> 01:02:30.202
l'm just dizzy, not deaf.

01:02:31.162 --> 01:02:33.242
Great. Smart ass. That's excellent.

01:02:33.362 --> 01:02:37.442
Did you see anything in here?
Any candy bars or something sweet?

01:02:38.043 --> 01:02:39.162
Let's check it again.

01:02:39.283 --> 01:02:40.602
Mom, l did it.

01:02:40.962 --> 01:02:42.762
We got to stay calm, okay?

01:02:42.843 --> 01:02:45.922
lf we stay calm, everything will be fine.
All right? Stay calm.

01:02:46.003 --> 01:02:47.483
You're making me nervous.

01:02:47.763 --> 01:02:49.283
l'm sorry.

01:02:50.923 --> 01:02:52.322
What if l keep dropping?

01:02:53.643 --> 01:02:56.283
You won't. l'll figure something out.

01:02:58.923 --> 01:03:00.403
You know, he's right.

01:03:01.323 --> 01:03:03.483
There's no way
we're getting into that room.

01:03:03.603 --> 01:03:05.083
What are you talking about?

01:03:06.483 --> 01:03:09.164
l just got to be honest with myself here.

01:03:09.844 --> 01:03:11.484
l don't need to be involved...

01:03:11.603 --> 01:03:15.243
...with anything so harrowing
or perilous at this point in my life.

01:03:15.324 --> 01:03:18.084
-You're giving up?
-Hell, yes.

01:03:18.324 --> 01:03:21.804
l don't need the fucking aggravation.
l'll make an anonymous phone call.

01:03:21.924 --> 01:03:25.884
They'll find the floor safe. l'll inherit.

01:03:26.924 --> 01:03:28.684
Stephen, Jeffrey, Catherine, David.

01:03:28.924 --> 01:03:32.164
Five grandkids, 60 percent inheritance tax.

01:03:32.324 --> 01:03:36.284
Fuck, l'll still put away 8 or 900 grand
and keep my goddamn hair.

01:03:37.244 --> 01:03:40.045
Take it. Go out and get loaded.

01:03:40.884 --> 01:03:42.605
Wait a minute.

01:03:43.605 --> 01:03:45.645
Say what you just said again.

01:03:51.324 --> 01:03:53.965
Say that shit about the money
again, babycakes.

01:03:54.965 --> 01:03:58.365
When? Before?

01:03:58.685 --> 01:03:59.925
Yeah, before.

01:04:00.045 --> 01:04:03.565
Splitting the money in your head,
you said you'd put away 800 or 900 grand.

01:04:04.965 --> 01:04:06.485
What are you doing?

01:04:06.605 --> 01:04:10.405
That was after tax, which makes it more
than a million and a half gross.

01:04:11.686 --> 01:04:14.006
So now you're a tax attorney.

01:04:16.685 --> 01:04:19.686
-l'm out of here.
-Wait a minute.

01:04:20.005 --> 01:04:24.206
There's sugar in everything.
Places you'd never expect. Like ketchup.

01:04:24.446 --> 01:04:25.806
Where else?

01:04:28.566 --> 01:04:30.206
Travel kit.

01:04:30.326 --> 01:04:32.966
Plus, you named eight people
you got to split it with...

01:04:33.046 --> 01:04:35.486
...so that's 10 or 12 million bucks
in the safe.

01:04:35.686 --> 01:04:38.686
A fuck-up like you has got to get less
than everybody else...

01:04:38.806 --> 01:04:40.686
...so now l don't know what to think.

01:04:41.126 --> 01:04:43.527
You're adding up money
you'll never touch, buddy.

01:04:44.607 --> 01:04:46.446
How much is in there?

01:04:48.567 --> 01:04:49.927
Mouthwash.

01:04:50.807 --> 01:04:51.687
Saccharin.

01:04:54.567 --> 01:04:57.047
Hey, l'm talking to you. Answer me.

01:04:57.527 --> 01:04:58.847
Fine. There's more.

01:04:59.647 --> 01:05:02.527
And when were you going to tell us
this minor economic detail?

01:05:02.647 --> 01:05:04.928
lt doesn't matter now.
lt's totally fucking moot!

01:05:05.807 --> 01:05:08.727
-Why are we having this conversation?
-What were you thinking?

01:05:08.847 --> 01:05:11.167
How did you expect to get away with this?

01:05:11.287 --> 01:05:13.288
Did you think that l'd open that safe...

01:05:13.408 --> 01:05:16.568
...and then me and Raoul would wait
while you picked out your share?

01:05:17.488 --> 01:05:19.247
What's the matter with you?

01:05:19.328 --> 01:05:22.247
You got us into this mess,
and you were going to fuck us?

01:05:22.328 --> 01:05:25.768
You got yourself into this.
You got the custody lawyers up your ass.

01:05:25.928 --> 01:05:28.528
Your eyes were huge
when l told you about the gig...

01:05:28.608 --> 01:05:29.968
...so don't play innocent.

01:05:30.568 --> 01:05:32.448
Things didn't work out.

01:05:33.848 --> 01:05:35.369
Play past it.

01:05:40.169 --> 01:05:42.288
Mints? Sugar-free.

01:05:42.329 --> 01:05:43.008
Mints? Sugar-free.

01:05:43.128 --> 01:05:46.489
l'm opening that safe.
You leave, you get nothing.

01:05:46.649 --> 01:05:48.409
lt's looking doubtful there, big guy.

01:05:48.529 --> 01:05:52.169
l will split the money with Raoul.
But l don't ever want to see you again.

01:05:52.288 --> 01:05:55.849
Cops show up on my doorstep,
we will know who sent them...

01:05:56.089 --> 01:05:58.089
...and we will fucking find you.

01:06:02.410 --> 01:06:03.729
l'll see you, Burnham.

01:06:04.969 --> 01:06:06.130
Later, Raoul.

01:06:12.130 --> 01:06:13.289
Mom!

01:06:21.690 --> 01:06:24.850
Ride in a Town Car to 125th Street
