01:41:23.283 --> 01:41:25.283
Freeze! Don't move, motherfucker!

01:41:25.922 --> 01:41:28.283
Don't move! l will kill you!

01:41:28.603 --> 01:41:30.003
Move away from the wall!

01:41:30.163 --> 01:41:32.963
Get off the fence! Move!

01:41:34.723 --> 01:41:36.763
Put your hands in the air!

01:41:36.963 --> 01:41:39.003
lt'll be okay. lt's fine, Dad.

01:41:41.083 --> 01:41:43.123
ls there anybody else in the house?

01:41:44.524 --> 01:41:45.364
No.

01:41:46.884 --> 01:41:50.404
Central, l need a bus at 38 West 94th.

01:41:57.124 --> 01:41:59.604
lt's okay. l'm all right.

01:42:03.884 --> 01:42:05.884
l want to see the palms of your hands!

01:42:06.044 --> 01:42:09.245
Do you hear me? Open your hands!

01:42:20.804 --> 01:42:24.205
Dad, it's okay. You're going to be fine.

01:42:24.325 --> 01:42:26.365
Everything is going to be fine.

01:42:56.246 --> 01:42:57.806
This sounds interesting.

01:42:57.926 --> 01:43:00.246
"Two-bedroom with den or third bedroom...

01:43:00.366 --> 01:43:03.686
"...new kitchen, original bath, 70s East."

01:43:04.966 --> 01:43:06.966
l thought you liked the West Side.

01:43:08.726 --> 01:43:10.527
"61st and Central Park West.

01:43:10.927 --> 01:43:14.527
"Bank foreclosure, must sell,
luxury doorman building, health club...

01:43:15.847 --> 01:43:17.846
-"...conserg--"
-Concierge.

01:43:18.207 --> 01:43:21.566
-What's that?
-lt's French for "superintendent."

01:43:22.246 --> 01:43:24.207
What's W.E.A. mean?

01:43:24.447 --> 01:43:25.967
That's West End Avenue.

01:43:26.407 --> 01:43:27.887
"81st and West End Avenue.

01:43:28.007 --> 01:43:31.367
"Three bedrooms plus den
or fourth bedroom, spacious living room...

01:43:31.607 --> 01:43:32.928
"...cathedral windows--"

01:43:33.007 --> 01:43:34.607
Do we need all that space?

01:43:38.528 --> 01:43:39.727
How about this?

01:43:39.967 --> 01:43:42.807
"West 83rd, two-bedroom,
doorman building...

01:43:43.247 --> 01:43:47.968
"...park block, partial views, bright and cheery,
high ceilings and wood floors."

01:43:48.339 --> 01:43:52.139
Yeah, that one. I like the sound
of that one.

